    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and cut your<strong> shallot[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>in half</p><p>Peel your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>green chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways and deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon)</p>",
